	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ex tuis literis scriptis 22. huius mensis adversam tuam valetudinem intellexi, quam contractam puto ex nimiis vigiliis et laboribus et intemperie aeris nimiaque humiditate.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">De ea magis sollicitus esse deberes.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Utinam mea opera aliquid in eius conservatione posset!</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sed spero dominum te sibi et suis firmiorem redditurum.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">De nostro rege spem magnam boni conceperunt regemque <placeName ref="l1209" cert="high">Navarre</placeName> sibi non defuturum et pacatiora omnia fore in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2464" cert="high">Gallia</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Forsan etiam rationes nonnullorum, qui multa moliebantur, conturbate manebunt.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Brevi nos certiora audiemus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Puer meus ad tuas respondet<note type="misc"><persName type="citizen_name" ref="p613" cert="high">M. Coignet d.J</persName>. an HB 26. Dez. 1560.</note></s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Octo abhinc diebus interrogabat eum mater, an vellet esse rex <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2464" cert="high">Gallie</placeName>; respondit se longe malle esse <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Bulingerum</persName>; valde est in te affectus.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Si ineunte vere possum in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2464" cert="high">Galliam</placeName> proficisci, remittam illum ad vos; optarem d. <persName ref="p8011" cert="high">Galterum</persName> eius curam vellet suscipere.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuto curabo, ut litere, quas misisti perferantur <persName type="auto_name">Aureliam</persName>, vellemque maiori in re animum erga te meum posse testari.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">D. <placeName type="auto_name">Redonensis</placeName> episcopus scripsit ad me spem esse magnam de consilio brevi futuro et intra paucos dies convocandos episcopos.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Stultus ille astrologus <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p20302" cert="high">Nostradamus</persName> inter infinita mendacia forsan verum dicet affirmans non fore consilium in anno proximo, sed verba inania.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salutat te uxor.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salutabis amicos omnes et nos amabis.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Te servet dominus incolumem.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l760" cert="high">Solut[uri]</placeName> 26. decembris.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuus ex animo <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p629" cert="high">Coignetius</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note>[von anderer Hand:]</note>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Domino <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Henrico Bullingero</persName>, ecclesiae Tigurinae pastori vigilantissimo.</s>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tiguri.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
